{"tid":446983,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"到底Air Asia買左平機票係咪焗硬你加錢選位呢","createTime":"2017-10-25T00:09:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T04:14:02.000Z","uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f33d02c8a063b70dcab58924b300703ad4ae68","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:09:22.000Z","msg":"小弟就飛online check-in先發現我張垃圾機票係冇得選位<br />\n我同女朋友去  結果可以玩到一個機頭一個機尾 <br />\n而架機係仲有好多空位既 <br />\n到底佢個system係咪焗住你加錢換位呢<br />\n定其實到時去counter可以叫佢幫手安排返？<br />\n求指教"},{"pid":"51f75f6ad65e8dd261dc86d46ecbfad44d1459d8","tid":446983,"uid":91146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:17:32.000Z","msg":"買平機票你預左 去counter 話要坐一齊 佢話一句選座位要額外比錢... 咁你都冇癮啦.."},{"pid":"df94776017e00e54bd020bf7481e1350ac02a467","tid":446983,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:18:27.000Z","msg":"先到先得"},{"pid":"2e73343779f327795a9ce36d16b9d35068d7234c","tid":446983,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T00:23:24.000Z","msg":"仆街因航都係咁<br />\n賣飛嗰陣又唔講明<br />\n有得揀位， 但係全部都單人位"},{"pid":"dee072aeaf3f72d6a9ee0d8218df424c5d761179","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先到先得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢一定唔係  仲有半架機空既"},{"pid":"cc141c625ffd08fcbc0a45ee787ed7c54d9c2224","tid":446983,"uid":148796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:15:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3a9f2799f5fa43e7cdb836d1c5228f02a15f239","tid":446983,"uid":148796,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:15:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1eb7e686fd124ab49b9dcf5fe07739103db1ed5","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買平機票你預左 去counter 話要坐一齊 佢話一句選座位要額外比錢... 咁你都冇癮啦..</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我真係要選窗邊 路口 多多要求要加錢我覺得合理既<br />\n加個錢唔係多<br />\n只係覺得你咁樣一個機頭一個機尾 會唔會太誇張<br />\n我一次過買得2張機票都係為左一齊坐姐<br />\n所以都好奇有冇其他人試過 <br />\n佢個system係咪真係咁乞衣焗9你加錢"},{"pid":"ed3014cc922a592660508f1616864a91693d0d0a","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>先到先得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢一定唔係  仲有半架機空既</blockquote><br />\n自己調啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上到架機自己坐過去?  <br />\n真係未試過  謝指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b80e3febb10cd4ec81461040ed3928f2d7f806f","tid":446983,"uid":41382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:19:42.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦，如果唔係點解會賣平機票比你"},{"pid":"c91ab80585bbfe2fdffbc5a97d9d457abee93967","tid":446983,"uid":148796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da02b4a6a75edb292d0a3f4d8e7f3fd721bed78c","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咁架啦，如果唔係點解會賣平機票比你</blockquote><br />\n通常廉航大把位揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉 我都係第一次遇到咁on9"},{"pid":"4397e72bd6168636731453fbe06cd4799edffc60","tid":446983,"uid":69302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"通常都會一齊坐 如果真係吉左咁多位 自己掉都無人理"},{"pid":"e3feb5ddb6ab8309958b237e7d6c4e9f205cbb88","tid":446983,"uid":148796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:27:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78bddf26530a9744153bbc1da6fa065a50f3a5b0","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常都會一齊坐 如果真係吉左咁多位 自己掉都無人理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇一睇  應該仲有5 60個位未有人選"},{"pid":"c566a344215a38953c41e585bcdd66a5bd92e3ce","tid":446983,"uid":148796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb0a3ba16fd0ef5ef93a030f2e4517b7c2af1c5b","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>通常都會一齊坐 如果真係吉左咁多位 自己掉都無人理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇一睇  應該仲有5 60個位未有人選</blockquote><br />\n搭得廉航冇咩人會加錢搞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔多想加 <br />\n但同條女去一個機頭一個機尾又真係好on9 <br />\n都認真諗緊屈唔屈服比錢搞"},{"pid":"f805b6b1ab0ef425c7b7ef476f75c0e96e3edab4","tid":446983,"uid":124949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T02:59:39.000Z","msg":"如果你買機票個陣無簡到位 唔係去到checkin 先分位嫁咩？地勤通常見你一齊checkin都會幫你地編坐埋一齊 <br />\n利申：搭過好多次都係一齊坐"},{"pid":"c92265bce988ad8dc041fec5c4b41d880b4fa077","tid":446983,"uid":20217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你買機票個陣無簡到位 唔係去到checkin 先分位嫁咩？地勤通常見你一齊checkin都會幫你地編坐埋一齊 <br />\n利申：搭過好多次都係一齊坐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我E家就係諗住online check in佢auto assign 左我地2個一頭一尾<br />\n姐係我地已經有位  <br />\n我即刻冇唔check in住  但佢都lock死左我地個位轉唔走"},{"pid":"071d365bd24bd118da4120d15d28d85b0b7d8e93","tid":446983,"uid":53601,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咁架啦，如果唔係點解會賣平機票比你</blockquote><br />\n通常廉航大把位揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉 我都係第一次遇到咁on9</blockquote><br />\n香港地勤一定係叫你加錢，好串</blockquote><br />\n我試過頂返個西面LCC地勤<br />\n又係叫我加錢之類<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「你㩒個enter喳喎？」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .......<br />\n<br />\n之後掂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca46beb3072213c8afb48c01b51e443194cb1401","tid":446983,"uid":62785,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:28:27.000Z","msg":"我真心佩服你班人<br />\n買廉航唔跟人地規則玩<br />\n有啲人就博下有無一齊坐<br />\n賭輸左走去屌地勤要免費轉一齊坐<br />\n點解地勤咁西我覺得你地貢獻不小<br />\n<br />\n有啲就話唔知原來無得揀位<br />\n無論咩原因都好<br />\n都係你自己既問題<br />\n人地規則寫撚定係度<br />\n你訂機票果陣無可能miss到佢叫你俾錢揀位果一欄<br />\n<br />\n無言"},{"pid":"71b87e5872450e51255b2f82b12cc7684cc0a79b","tid":446983,"uid":62785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"仲講到屈唔屈服真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ef7a1eb9b66302b59581ac17b62ca8e609c5d7","tid":446983,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲講到屈唔屈服真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCan't agger more <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345ec1189366c0af4f8eed1f9e769b262b5c1c57","tid":446983,"uid":53037,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"買得平機票人地就係預你買其他service 例如揀位黎賺錢<br />\n咁介意驚無得坐埋一齊又唔肯俾錢<br />\n乞衣到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661513cd32b60abf60c2e623587a6a0bdb95ec4e","tid":446983,"uid":53037,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲講到屈唔屈服真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCan't agger more <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好肉酸<br />\n香港客成日俾人話西就係多得呢班人"}]}